ization of highly absorbing layers. We also report on\nthe requirements that a 10B4C layer must fulfill in order to be employed as a\nconverter in neutron detection.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 5 Oct 2015 10:08:17 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-10-31"}
